# Subtitle Player — Environment Example

Copy to the repository root as `.env`, or for the packaged desktop app to `%APPDATA%\SubtitlePlayer\.env`.

```ini
# ── DashScope (Alibaba Cloud Bailian) — recommended for translation ─────────
DASHSCOPE_OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1
DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=sk-your-dashscope-key-here
TRANSLATE_MODEL=qwen3.6-flash

# ── Optional: generic OpenAI-compatible fallback ───────────────────────────
# Used when DashScope vars are missing (via scripts.lib get_llm_config).
# BASE_URL=https://api.example.com/v1
# API_KEY=sk-your-key-here
```

**Notes**

- Only variables needed for translation are listed here. The parent repo `.env.example` covers STT and summarization.
- After changing API key or base URL, **restart** the server. Model parameters in the ⚙ UI apply without restart.
- Lookup order: exe directory → `%APPDATA%\SubtitlePlayer\.env` → project root `.env`.
